data.title: Animation
data.meta_description: Explore the NFB’s vast animated film collection by director or via curated features and watch new, timely and award-winning Canadian animation online.
data.text:
New - Meditate on the dualities of life

Don't Let the Sun Catch You Crying

Witness the transformative ability of art to elevate and transcend us in this poetic animated doc, a collaboration between mother, elder and narrator Edith Almadi and directors Natalie Baird and Toby Gillies.
